# Public Layout

Entry page: **`/onboarding`** (`src/routes/(public)/onboarding/`). Root `/` redirects there.

Shared shell in `(public)/+layout.svelte`:

- [`PublicNavbar.svelte`](src/lib/components/PublicNavbar.svelte) ‚Äî DaisyUI `navbar`
- [`PublicFooter.svelte`](src/lib/components/PublicFooter.svelte) ‚Äî DaisyUI `footer`

Path constant: [`src/lib/constants/public-routes.ts`](src/lib/constants/public-routes.ts)

Auth pages under `(public)/auth/` inherit the same navbar and footer.

